  BETTER_AO_BACKEND_HOST  Backend bind host. Default: 127.0.0.1
  BETTER_AO_BACKEND_PORT  Preferred backend port. Default: 7331
  VITE_PORT               Preferred web port. Default: web/.env or 3000

